Use Case: RepairShip
Scope: BattleShip
Primary Actor: User
Intention: The User wants to repair a damaged ship.
Level: Subfunction
Multiplicity: The User can only repair a ship once per
              turn per game.
Main Success Scenario:
  1. User selects a ship and informs System.
  2. System highlights selected ship and displays menu of actions.
  3. User selects "repair ship" from menu.
  6. System verifies the ship is touching the base and is damaged.
     Use Case ends in success.
Extensions:
  1-5a. User informs System he would like to make a different move.
        Use Case ends in success.
  3-5. User informs System he would like to select a different ship.
       Use Case continues at step 1.
  6a. System informs User he cannot repair this ship because it is
      not touching his base.
      Use Case continues at step 3.
  6a. System informs User he cannot repair this ship because it is
      not damaged.
      Use Case continues at step 3.
